title: Joe Bonamassa - Muddy Wolf at Red Rocks 2014 - 1080p AC3
description:
Joe Bonamassa - Muddy Wolf at Red Rocks 2014 - 1080p AC3

Performed August 31, 2014 at the Red Rocks Amphitheater, Morrison, Colorado

This video was broadcast on March 6 on public television. It is a shortened promotional "teaser" for the upcoming 2-DVD/Blue-Ray release on March 26,2015. The actual product release is expected to be much longer and of far better quality.

The concert is a celebration of the Blues legends Muddy Waters and Howlin' Wolf with a tribute featuring both musicians' song catalogs followed by Joe's own set of songs. The video includes short clips of Muddy Waters and Howlin' Wolf interviews and performances.
